<h4 id="galois">Galois</h4>
<p>I want to make function pointer void(func*) make sense.</p>
<ul>
  <li>integer pointer int* p</li>
  <li>void pointer void*</li>
  <li>void funtion pointer void(func*)(std::string a)</li>
</ul>

